Example of YAML input to the MDS
================================

xpl-family is a YAML example. Input files are:

 - xpl-family/FE/YAML/xpl/xpl1/Description.yml: trimmed down description of a VLIW processor.

 - Opcode.txt: The opcode map, automatically built from Description.yml.

 - xpl-family/FE/YAML/BIN/makeBundle.pl: Perl script used to generate Bundle.yml file.


